title: Lobby
introMessage:
Welcome to Cyberdyne!


QUICK START: Click on a bot and challenge them to a randombattle.

All the +users in this room are bots. Challenge them and they will accept.
Click their names to see what battle types they prefer.
ex. randomb-bot picks moves at random and never switches.
la-stabby/ picks moves that do the most damage to you.
LA-RED531 is the most recent Gauntlet winner.
Have fun & try new things!
